{"tid":1433860,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"急推！！地區教育好重要！","createTime":"2019-08-08T15:07:25.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-08T15:33:50.000Z","uid":159380,"like":11,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"89e108677a71562ecebff1411396158c6068bbf8","tid":1433860,"uid":159380,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-08T15:07:25.000Z","msg":"現階段<strong><span style=\"font-size: large;\">地區教育</span></strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">好重要</span></strong></span>！！<br />\n<br />\n小弟前前後後擺左成個月街站<br />\n<br />\n由一開始到依家都聽到好多街坊意見都覺得街站形式好好 用一個和理非既形式做到宣傳效果<br />\n只要有禮貌少少 好多人願意拎傳單睇下<br />\n特別係中年老年戈班！ <br />\n街站係好好既機會解釋俾佢地聽發生咩事<br />\n最緊要係可以打翻<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong>形象牌</strong></span> <br />\n<br />\n但見到呢場運動開始越耐就越少街站 <br />\n希望大家可以出一分力去組織朋友仔或者志同道合既朋友一齊印d文宣擺下街站！<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">勇武同和理非 缺一不可！ </span></strong><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">天佑香港！</span></strong></span>"},{"pid":"f056d8736e66cda454822f78708491b5075602b6","tid":1433860,"uid":265339,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-08T15:07:45.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"b2c127b4e58acb81d3d464964b0ddeccfaee6094","tid":1433860,"uid":202909,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-08T15:17:25.000Z","msg":"唔好意思阻一阻你<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/OsrWGAr.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FOsrWGAr.png&h=fa3ea537&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"db7a34c144ef0bbe9c5d485c2c78049721685e5b","tid":1433860,"uid":144942,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-08T15:17:41.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"23e6cb9a794311eef5372314953cebbfe49b62ac","tid":1433860,"uid":159380,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-08T15:21:11.000Z","msg":"推！"},{"pid":"33ab88fde0c51871d7f620fe4ba40166a8a1d60a","tid":1433860,"uid":159380,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-08T15:21:24.000Z","msg":"推！"},{"pid":"a1eedd047a354b88861a0cf20143b7bafd7c8b27","tid":1433860,"uid":159380,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-08T15:21:34.000Z","msg":"自推！"},{"pid":"72663b805e314a95d78585404dae3578d7b56473","tid":1433860,"uid":280452,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-08T15:27:36.000Z","msg":"簡單黎講<br />\n你一定要乖仔女樣 點都唔可以發老脾<br />\n咁時不時有兩類人會挑你機<br />\n<br />\n一類係無得救既廢藍 <br />\n你望住佢笑唔使理佢就得 <br />\n佢一係就無印走，一係就忍唔住郁手<br />\n佢郁手就幫拖捉佢打人 <br />\n佢唔係襲擊既小動作就唔使理佢<br />\n鬧咁耐一定有人圍觀拍片， 自己人旁邊一定要拍片<br />\n<br />\n第二類係自以為好有智慧既師奶或中老人<br />\n佢地會問你問題 怪你阻人之類<br />\n答呢d問題 一定要夠現實 唔可以講理想化既野<br />\n或者帶佢去番港共破壞既野係遠遠多於所謂示威既破壞論點<br />\n同埋要表現出歉意，迫於無奈先咁做，覺得好唔好意思"},{"pid":"c7117d200b646525294e50e5856207e8257f83e1","tid":1433860,"uid":45259,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-08T15:31:37.000Z","msg":"好支持"},{"pid":"6864397cad0ff612424ce37ffa86f0862ad88aba","tid":1433860,"uid":45259,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-08T15:31:58.000Z","msg":"由放映會再開始"},{"pid":"3c8e34cbd95cf25fe8608005d9940ad4f161edfe","tid":1433860,"uid":45259,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-08T15:32:10.000Z","msg":"啲文宣停咗好耐"},{"pid":"739bc1b0128d9000b34978762caf992eeab9b879","tid":1433860,"uid":45259,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-08T15:32:30.000Z","msg":"不過唔停得架<br />\n要長期keep住"},{"pid":"2abb04cf22d4f8ba2096474b9ca453d2ee3146e5","tid":1433860,"uid":294052,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-08T15:33:50.000Z","msg":"夠唔夠人手做足18區"}]}